General.Name: HORNBACH Baumarkt AG
General.Description: HORNBACH Baumarkt AG operates as a do-it-yourself (DIY) retail company in Germany, Austria, the Czech Republic, Luxembourg, the Netherlands, Romania, Slovakia, Sweden, and Switzerland. It operates through Retail and Real Estate segments. The company offers various products in the hardware / electrical, paint / wallpaper / flooring, construction materials / timber / prefabricated components, sanitary / tiles, and garden hardware/plants divisions. It also owns and rents retail properties and logistics center. The company was founded in 1877 and is based in Bornheim, Germany. HORNBACH Baumarkt AG is a subsidiary of Hornbach Holding AG & Co. KGaA.
